            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I don't think I can really sum up my feelings for Harvard House in a few words but to be precise, Harvard House has instilled in me the qualities that I know would be beneficial for me in this sweet-sour journey of life.\nIt gave me a platform to explore myself: my attributes and skills and it's nothing but the culmination of all these bcoz of which I managed to clear my ICSE with 94.4% from Harvard House.\nThe bonding that I shared with the students as well as the staff is just impeccable.\nI thank the school management and the staff for encouraging the students to unlock their true potential.\nA special thank I would like to convey to that teacher whose presence in my life helped me a lot in grooming up and she is none other than Mrs Ranjana Das. ",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
